surf_spacedout

This is a space based map which i have been working on the past week, and finally it is out for you all. The custom models and skyboxes are pakratted so you don't have to worry about any .res files.

The map was compiled with RAD, not another fullbright map.

Comments are always welcome.

Enjoy!

--Buck
http://forums.solidsurf.info/
